        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your internal chemical balance is adaptable, allowing you to control the composition of your normally flaming expulsions. When you use @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.ancestry-features.Item.Fire Breath], you can choose to deal acid or cold damage instead of fire damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you're a mystic with the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.class-features.Item.Elemental] connection, you can also choose bludgeoning, electricity, or poison damage instead of fire damage.</p>"
